REPORTS_ITEM.REPORT_NAME: UMGMT Usage Statistics: Website Year Month

T_REPORT_PARAM.PARAM_TEXT: Start Date (Default is current date - 30 days)

T_REPORT_SQL.SQL_TEXT: select u.user_id, u.un from users u join user_sec_role usr on (usr.user_id = u.user_id) join sec_role sr on ( sr.sec_role_id = usr.sec_role_id and sr.role_type = 'Never_Expire' )

with usage_log_logins as ( select user_id, iis_start from usage_log where action_id = 1 /*Logon*/ ), usage_log_logins_min as ( select min(iis_start) miniis_start from usage_log_logins ), usage_log_logins_max as ( select max(iis_start) maxiis_start from usage_log_logins ), usage_log_logins_mtom as ( select to_char(add_months(miniis_start, level - 1), 'MON') month, to_char(add_months(miniis_start, level - 1), 'YYYY') year, to_date(to_char(add_months(miniis_start, level - 1), 'MON') || '/' || to_char(add_months(miniis_start, level - 1), 'YYYY'), 'MM/YYYY') start_date, to_date(to_char(add_months(miniis_start, level - 1 + 1), 'MON') || '/' || to_char(add_months(miniis_start, level - 1 + 1), 'YYYY'), 'MM/YYYY') - 1/24/60/60 end_date from usage_log_logins_min join usage_log_logins_max on (1 = 1) connect by level <= round(months_between(maxiis_start, miniis_start)) + 1 ), user_since as ( select distinct u.user_id, min(alc.ts) ts from users u join audit_log_comp_main_pk alcmp on (alcmp.pk_value = u.user_id) join audit_log_comp alc on ( alcmp.audit_log_comp_id = alc.audit_log_comp_id and alc.table_name = 'USERS' ) group by u.user_id ), user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date as ( select ulov.month, ulov.year, count(u.user_id) cnt, u.is_disabled, case when lower(u.email) like '%onevizion.com%' then 0 else 1 end ov_cus from usage_log_logins_mtom ulov join users u on (1 = 1) join user_since us on (us.user_id = u.user_id) where us.ts < ulov.end_date group by ulov.month, ulov.year, ulov.start_date, ulov.end_date, u.is_disabled, case when lower(u.email) like '%onevizion.com%' then 0 else 1 end ), usage_log_logins_ov_cus as ( select ul.user_id, ul.iis_start, case when lower(u.email) like '%onevizion.com%' then 0 else 1 end ov_cus from usage_log_logins ul join users u on (u.user_id = ul.user_id) ), usage_log_logins_ov_cus_count as ( select ul.ov_cus, um.month, um.year, count(distinct ul.user_id) count_unique from usage_log_logins_ov_cus ul join usage_log_logins_mtom um on (ul.iis_start between um.start_date and um.end_date) group by ul.ov_cus, um.month, um.year )
select nvl(unove.cnt, 0) "Non-OV Enabled Users", nvl(unovd.cnt, 0) "Non-OV Disabled Users", nvl(ulcus.count_unique, 0) "Non-OV Users-Unique-Logins", nvl(uove.cnt, 0) "OV Enabled Users", nvl(uovd.cnt, 0) "OV Disabled Users", nvl(ulov.count_unique, 0) "OV Users-Unique-Logins", ulov.year "Year", ulov.month "Month" from usage_log_logins_ov_cus_count ulov left join usage_log_logins_ov_cus_count ulcus on ( ulcus.month = ulov.month and ulcus.year = ulov.year and ulcus.ov_cus = 1 ) left join user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date unove on ( unove.month = ulov.month and unove.year = ulov.year and unove.is_disabled = 0 and unove.ov_cus = 1 ) left join user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date unovd on ( unovd.month = ulov.month and unovd.year = ulov.year and unovd.is_disabled = 1 and unovd.ov_cus = 1 ) left join user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date uove on ( uove.month = ulov.month and uove.year = ulov.year and uove.is_disabled = 0 and uove.ov_cus = 0 ) left join user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date uovd on ( uovd.month = ulov.month and uovd.year = ulov.year and uovd.is_disabled = 1 and uovd.ov_cus = 0 ) where ulov.ov_cus = 0 order by to_date(ulov.month || '/' || ulov.year, 'MM/YYYY') desc

select distinct user_id "user id", un "user name", case when lower(email) not like '%onevizion.com%' then 'Customer' else 'OV' end "ov/customer", case when is_disabled = 1 then 'Yes' else 'No' end "is disabled right now", case when ts is null then 'No' else 'Yes' end "Mobile login" from (select u.user_id, u.un, u.email, u.is_disabled, ulb.ts from users u left join usage_log ul on ( ul.user_id = u.user_id ) left join usage_log_browser ulb on ( ulb.usage_log_browser_id = ul.usage_log_browser_id ) where u.is_disabled = 0 union select distinct u.user_id, u.un, u.email, u.is_disabled, ulb.ts from users u join audit_log_comp_main_pk alcmp on (alcmp.pk_value = u.user_id) join audit_log_comp alc on ( alcmp.audit_log_comp_id = alc.audit_log_comp_id and alc.table_name = 'USERS' and alc.ts between nvl(to_date(:start_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(add_months(current_date, -1), 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) and nvl(to_date(:end_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(current_date, 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) ) join audit_log_comp_col alcc on ( alcc.audit_log_comp_id = alc.audit_log_comp_id and alcc.column_name = 'IS_DISABLED' ) join audit_log_comp_col_un_val alccuv on ( alccuv.audit_log_comp_col_id = alcc.audit_log_comp_col_id and to_number(alccuv.new_val) = 1 ) left join usage_log ul on ( ul.user_id = u.user_id ) left join usage_log_browser ulb on ( ulb.usage_log_browser_id = ul.usage_log_browser_id ) where u.is_disabled = 1 )

with usage_log_logins as ( select ul.user_id, ul.iis_start, ulb.ts from usage_log ul left join usage_log_browser ulb on ( ulb.usage_log_browser_id = ul.usage_log_browser_id ) where action_id = 1 /*Logon*/ ), count_usage_log_logins as ( select user_id, count(iis_start) iis_start, max(ts) last_login_mobile from usage_log_logins where iis_start between nvl(to_date(:start_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(add_months(current_date, -1), 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) and nvl(to_date(:end_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(current_date, 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) group by user_id ), user_since as ( select distinct u.user_id, min(alc.ts) ts from users u join audit_log_comp_main_pk alcmp on (alcmp.pk_value = u.user_id) join audit_log_comp alc on ( alcmp.audit_log_comp_id = alc.audit_log_comp_id and alc.table_name = 'USERS' ) group by u.user_id )
select u.user_id, u.un, u.email, case when lower(u.email) not like '%onevizion.com%' then 'Customer' else 'OV' end "OV/Customer", to_char(m.ts, 'MM/DD/YYYY') "USER_SINCE", nvl(c.iis_start, 0) "Number of Logins", decode(u.is_disabled, 1, 'No', 0, 'Yes') "Enabled", to_char(u.last_login_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY') "Last Login-Web", to_char(c.last_login_mobile, 'MM/DD/YYYY') "Last Login-Mobile" from users u left join user_since m on (m.user_id = u.user_id) left join count_usage_log_logins c on (c.user_id = u.user_id)

select trunc(api_calls.iis_start, 'MON') mnth, api_calls.url endpoint_url, api_calls.platform, api_calls.method http_method, count(*) quantity from (select regexp_replace(regexp_replace(t_ul.url, '\?.+', ''), '/[[:digit:]]+', '/XXX') url, t_ul.un, case when t_auth_token.device_id like 'UUID:%' then 'Android' when t_auth_token.device_id = 'N/A' or t_auth_token.device_id is null then 'N/A' else 'iOS' end as platform, t_method.name method, t_ul.iis_start iis_start from usage_log t_ul left join auth_token t_auth_token on ( t_auth_token.access_key = t_ul.auth_token_access_key ) join http_request_method t_method on ( t_method.http_request_method_id = t_ul.http_request_method_id ) where t_ul.action_id = 3 and t_ul.iis_start between nvl(to_date(:start_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(add_months(current_date, -1), 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) and nvl(to_date(:end_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(current_date, 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) and (instr(t_ul.url, '/api/wf') <> 0 or t_ul.url = '/api/v3/server_info') and instr(t_ul.url, '/changed_fields') = 0) api_calls group by api_calls.url, api_calls.platform, api_calls.method, trunc(api_calls.iis_start, 'MON') order by trunc(api_calls.iis_start, 'MON') desc

select distinct user_id "user id", un "user name", case when lower(email) not like '%onevizion.com%' then 'Customer' else 'OV' end "ov/customer", case when is_disabled = 1 then 'Yes' else 'No' end "is disabled right now", case when ts is null then 'No' else 'Yes' end "Mobile login" from (select u.user_id, u.un, u.email, u.is_disabled, ulb.ts from users u left join usage_log ul on ( ul.user_id = u.user_id ) left join usage_log_browser ulb on ( ulb.usage_log_browser_id = ul.usage_log_browser_id ) where u.is_disabled = 0 union select distinct u.user_id, u.un, u.email, u.is_disabled, ulb.ts from users u join audit_log_comp_main_pk alcmp on (alcmp.pk_value = u.user_id) join audit_log_comp alc on ( alcmp.audit_log_comp_id = alc.audit_log_comp_id and alc.table_name = 'USERS' and alc.ts between nvl(to_date(:start_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(add_months(current_date, -1), 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) and nvl(to_date(:end_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(current_date, 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) ) join audit_log_comp_col alcc on ( alcc.audit_log_comp_id = alc.audit_log_comp_id and alcc.column_name = 'IS_DISABLED' ) join audit_log_comp_col_un_val alccuv on ( alccuv.audit_log_comp_col_id = alcc.audit_log_comp_col_id and to_number(alccuv.new_val) = 1 ) left join usage_log ul on ( ul.user_id = u.user_id ) left join usage_log_browser ulb on ( ulb.usage_log_browser_id = ul.usage_log_browser_id ) where u.is_disabled = 1 )

with usage_log_logins as ( select ul.user_id, ul.iis_start, ulb.ts from usage_log ul left join usage_log_browser ulb on ( ulb.usage_log_browser_id = ul.usage_log_browser_id ) where action_id = 1 /*Logon*/ ), count_usage_log_logins as ( select user_id, count(iis_start) iis_start, max(ts) last_login_mobile from usage_log_logins where iis_start between nvl(to_date(:start_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(add_months(current_date, -1), 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) and nvl(to_date(:end_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(current_date, 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) group by user_id ), user_since as ( select distinct u.user_id, min(alc.ts) ts from users u join audit_log_comp_main_pk alcmp on (alcmp.pk_value = u.user_id) join audit_log_comp alc on ( alcmp.audit_log_comp_id = alc.audit_log_comp_id and alc.table_name = 'USERS' ) group by u.user_id )
select u.user_id, u.un, u.email, case when lower(u.email) not like '%onevizion.com%' then 'Customer' else 'OV' end "OV/Customer", to_char(m.ts, 'MM/DD/YYYY') "USER_SINCE", nvl(c.iis_start, 0) "Number of Logins", decode(u.is_disabled, 1, 'No', 0, 'Yes') "Enabled", to_char(u.last_login_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY') "Last Login-Web", to_char(c.last_login_mobile, 'MM/DD/YYYY') "Last Login-Mobile" from users u left join user_since m on (m.user_id = u.user_id) left join count_usage_log_logins c on (c.user_id = u.user_id)

select trunc(api_calls.iis_start, 'MON') mnth, api_calls.url endpoint_url, api_calls.platform, api_calls.method http_method, count(*) quantity from (select regexp_replace(regexp_replace(t_ul.url, '\?.+', ''), '/[[:digit:]]+', '/XXX') url, t_ul.un, case when t_auth_token.device_id like 'UUID:%' then 'Android' when t_auth_token.device_id = 'N/A' or t_auth_token.device_id is null then 'N/A' else 'iOS' end as platform, t_method.name method, t_ul.iis_start iis_start from usage_log t_ul left join auth_token t_auth_token on ( t_auth_token.access_key = t_ul.auth_token_access_key ) join http_request_method t_method on ( t_method.http_request_method_id = t_ul.http_request_method_id ) where t_ul.action_id = 3 and t_ul.iis_start between nvl(to_date(:start_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(add_months(current_date, -1), 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) and nvl(to_date(:end_date, 'MM/DD/YYYY'), to_date(to_char(current_date, 'MM/YYYY') || '/01', 'MM/YYYY/DD')) and (instr(t_ul.url, '/api/wf') <> 0 or t_ul.url = '/api/v3/server_info') and instr(t_ul.url, '/changed_fields') = 0) api_calls group by api_calls.url, api_calls.platform, api_calls.method, trunc(api_calls.iis_start, 'MON') order by trunc(api_calls.iis_start, 'MON') desc
select u.user_id, u.un from users u join user_sec_role usr on (usr.user_id = u.user_id) join sec_role sr on ( sr.sec_role_id = usr.sec_role_id and sr.role_type = 'Never_Expire' )

with usage_log_logins as ( select user_id, iis_start from usage_log where action_id = 1 /*Logon*/ ), usage_log_logins_min as ( select min(iis_start) miniis_start from usage_log_logins ), usage_log_logins_max as ( select max(iis_start) maxiis_start from usage_log_logins ), usage_log_logins_mtom as ( select to_char(add_months(miniis_start, level - 1 + 1), 'MON') || '/' || to_char(add_months(miniis_start, level - 1 + 1), 'YYYY'), 'MM/YYYY') - 1/24/60/60 end_date from usage_log_logins_min join usage_log_logins_max on (1 = 1) connect by level <= round(months_between(maxiis_start, miniis_start)) + 1 ), user_since as ( select distinct u.user_id, min(alc.ts) ts from users u join audit_log_comp_main_pk alcmp on (alcmp.pk_value = u.user_id) join audit_log_comp alc on ( alcmp.audit_log_comp_id = alc.audit_log_comp_id and alc.table_name = 'USERS' ) group by u.user_id ), user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date as ( select ulov.month, ulov.year, count(u.user_id) cnt, u.is_disabled, case when lower(u.email) like '%onevizion.com%' then 0 else 1 end ov_cus from usage_log_logins_mtom ulov join users u on (1 = 1) join user_since us on (us.user_id = u.user_id) where us.ts < ulov.end_date group by ulov.month, ulov.year, ulov.start_date, ulov.end_date, u.is_disabled, case when lower(u.email) like '%onevizion.com%' then 0 else 1 end ), usage_log_logins_ov_cus as ( select ul.user_id, ul.iis_start, case when lower(u.email) like '%onevizion.com%' then 0 else 1 end ov_cus from usage_log_logins ul join users u on (u.user_id = ul.user_id) ), usage_log_logins_ov_cus_count as ( select ul.ov_cus, um.month, um.year, count(distinct ul.user_id) count_unique from usage_log_logins_ov_cus ul join usage_log_logins_mtom um on (ul.iis_start between um.start_date and um.end_date) group by ul.ov_cus, um.month, um.year )
select nvl(unove.cnt, 0) "Non-OV Enabled Users", nvl(unovd.cnt, 0) "Non-OV Disabled Users", nvl(ulcus.count_unique, 0) "Non-OV Users-Unique-Logins", nvl(uove.cnt, 0) "OV Enabled Users", nvl(uovd.cnt, 0) "OV Disabled Users", nvl(ulov.count_unique, 0) "OV Users-Unique-Logins", ulov.year "Year", ulov.month "Month" from usage_log_logins_ov_cus_count ulov left join usage_log_logins_ov_cus_count ulcus on ( ulcus.month = ulov.month and ulcus.year = ulov.year and ulcus.ov_cus = 1 ) left join user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date unove on ( unove.month = ulov.month and unove.year = ulov.year and unove.is_disabled = 0 and unove.ov_cus = 1 ) left join user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date unovd on ( unovd.month = ulov.month and unovd.year = ulov.year and unovd.is_disabled = 1 and unovd.ov_cus = 1 ) left join user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date uove on ( uove.month = ulov.month and uove.year = ulov.year and uove.is_disabled = 0 and uove.ov_cus = 0 ) left join user_novov_ov_dis_enab_date uovd on ( uovd.month = ulov.month and uovd.year = ulov.year and uovd.is_disabled = 1 and uovd.ov_cus = 0 ) where ulov.ov_cus = 0 order by to_date(ulov.month || '/' || ulov.year, 'MM/YYYY') desc
